Section 8 says,

21:08.740 --> 21:11.180
these traces are weakly interacting.

21:11.740 --> 21:14.160
This is clearly an attempt to explain

21:14.160 --> 21:15.980
the cosmic neutrino background

21:15.980 --> 21:18.280
without a hot Big Bang.

21:18.280 --> 21:19.600
And it works.

21:19.600 --> 21:22.120
The equation shows that

21:22.120 --> 21:24.240
nu records the integrated

21:24.240 --> 21:25.880
scalar amplification.

21:26.640 --> 21:28.200
It's a retarded integral.

21:28.860 --> 21:30.300
It naturally produces

21:30.300 --> 21:32.920
a background of fossilized entropy.

21:33.780 --> 21:35.340
It explains the observations

21:35.340 --> 21:37.560
without requiring the universe

21:37.560 --> 21:38.780
to have been compressed

21:38.780 --> 21:40.140
into a singularity

21:40.140 --> 21:41.820
13 billion years ago.

21:42.240 --> 21:43.800
It essentially says

21:43.800 --> 21:44.860
the background radiation

21:44.860 --> 21:47.440
is the exhaust of the creation engine.

21:47.440 --> 21:50.220
It explains them

