21:55.620 --> 21:56.980
It feels like reverse engineering.

21:57.560 --> 21:58.400
You need the background

21:58.400 --> 21:59.800
so you invent a registry

21:59.800 --> 22:00.520
to store it.

22:00.880 --> 22:01.920
You need the structure

22:01.920 --> 22:02.840
so you invent

22:02.840 --> 22:04.100
an engine to build it.

22:04.600 --> 22:06.080
It's mathematically coherent,

22:06.240 --> 22:06.920
I'll give you that.

22:07.280 --> 22:08.700
But it feels constructed.

22:09.380 --> 22:10.560
I think you are being

22:10.560 --> 22:12.900
uncharitable to the elegance

22:12.900 --> 22:15.220
of the bifurcation analysis.

22:15.680 --> 22:18.020
Look, the choice is this.

22:18.580 --> 22:20.720
Either space itself stretches,

22:21.180 --> 22:23.080
which we cannot mechanically explain,

22:23.480 --> 22:25.680
we just label it dark energy,

22:25.940 --> 22:28.220
or the fields within space

22:28.220 --> 22:30.580
undergo thermodynamic evolution.

22:31.440 --> 22:32.680
This paper provides

22:32.680 --> 22:34.320
the first rigorous proof

22:34.320 --> 22:35.560
that the latter is possible.

22:36.020 --> 22:36.540
Possible?

22:36.960 --> 22:37.400
Maybe?

22:37.860 --> 22:38.560
Probable?

22:38.880 --> 22:39.820
I'm not convinced.

22:39.820 --> 22:41.560
But the cost of this model

22:41.560 --> 22:43.040
is living in a universe

22:43.040 --> 22:44.960
where the laws of thermodynamics

22:44.960 --> 22:46.600
can locally invert.

22:47.220 --> 22:48.520
I see we are reaching

22:48.520 --> 22:49.260
the boundary

22:49.260 --> 22:51.600
of our own effective diffusion here.

22:52.160 --> 22:52.640
Indeed.

22:53.160 --> 22:55.100
To summarize my position,

22:56.020 --> 22:57.120
scalar eruption

22:57.120 --> 22:59.520
via entropic differential

22:59.520 --> 23:01.740
offers a mathematically

23:01.740 --> 23:03.560
rigorous path to structure

23:03.560 --> 23:04.680
that respects

23:04.680 --> 23:06.460
the conservation of mass,

23:06.900 --> 23:08.500
as detailed in Section 15,

23:08.500 --> 23:09.820
and replaces

23:09.820 --> 23:12.560
the clumsy metric expansion

23:12.560 --> 23:14.100
with precise

23:14.100 --> 23:15.980
entropic differentials.

23:16.760 --> 23:18.880
It unifies information theory

23:18.880 --> 23:19.960
with geometry.

23:20.240 --> 23:21.620
It tells us that the universe

23:21.620 --> 23:22.860
isn't blowing up

23:22.860 --> 23:23.480
like a balloon.

23:23.900 --> 23:24.920
It's crystallizing

23:24.920 --> 23:25.680
like a diamond.

23:26.240 --> 23:28.060
And my position remains

23:28.060 --> 23:29.900
that while the bifurcation analysis

23:29.900 --> 23:31.280
is impressive on paper,

23:31.480 --> 23:33.320
the physical cost is too high.

23:33.760 --> 23:34.640
You are asking us

23:34.640 --> 23:35.840
to accept a universe

23:35.840 --> 23:37.480
driven by negative diffusion

23:37.480 --> 23:38.900
and vacuum instability.

23:39.480 --> 23:40.820
The five-engine system

23:40.820 --> 23:41.600
is an intricate,

23:41.860 --> 23:42.580
fragile machine

23:42.580 --> 23:43.380
designed to keep

23:43.380 --> 23:44.260
a static universe

23:44.260 --> 23:45.120
from collapsing

23:45.120 --> 23:45.880
under its own

23:45.880 --> 23:46.860
mathematical weight.

23:47.320 --> 23:47.780
Yet,

23:47.960 --> 23:49.620
we both must agree

23:49.620 --> 23:50.860
that Flaxion

23:50.860 --> 23:52.540
has successfully challenged

23:52.540 --> 23:53.260
the assumption

23:53.260 --> 23:54.560
that expansion

23:54.560 --> 23:56.120
is the only way

23:56.120 --> 23:56.980
to explain

23:56.980 --> 23:58.280
distance and structure.

23:58.620 --> 23:59.120
Absolutely.

23:59.760 --> 24:00.880
It forces us

24:00.880 --> 24:02.220
to look at the equations

24:02.220 --> 24:03.020
and ask,

24:03.580 --> 24:05.260
is redshift geometry

24:05.260 --> 24:06.980
or is it entropy?

24:07.540 --> 24:08.400
It leaves us

24:08.400 --> 24:09.060
with the image

24:09.060 --> 24:10.960
of a breathing static plenum

24:10.960 --> 24:12.420
locally erupting

24:12.420 --> 24:13.120
and freezing

24:13.120 --> 24:14.960
through thermodynamic pressure.

24:15.380 --> 24:17.000
It's a haunting image,

24:17.320 --> 24:18.880
even if I don't buy the physics.

24:19.240 --> 24:20.280
A haunting image

24:20.280 --> 24:21.820
for a haunting cosmos.

24:22.640 --> 24:24.120
That is all the time we have.

24:24.480 --> 24:25.400
Check your local

24:25.400 --> 24:27.020
entropy curvature, everyone.

24:27.420 --> 24:29.040
This is The Debate.

